OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry with spells of cloudy
OL,6,Fweather interspersed with periods of
OL,7,Fsunshine, these most prolonged during
OL,8,Fthe afternoon. Somewhat warmer than on
OL,9,FMonday, though increasingly breezy
OL,10,Fwith an easterly wind developing, this
OL,11,Fbecoming gusty in places.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FClear and dry overnight, with
OL,14,Fsome patchy cloud developing across
OL,15,Feastern counties later. Chilly
OL,16,Fovernight, perhaps with a touch of
OL,17,Ffrost in some sheltered rural spots.
OL,18,FRemaining blustery.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
