OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FA chilly start on Wednesday
OL,6,Fwith any cloud soon lifting to leave a
OL,7,Fsunny day with plenty of strong April
OL,8,Fsunshine. Warmer than recent days,
OL,9,Fdespite the breezy conditions.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FDry
OL,12,Fthrough the remainder of the week with
OL,13,Fhigh pressure dominating. Often sunny
OL,14,Fand feeling warm by day. Chilly nights
OL,15,Fwith rural frosts possible as winds
OL,16,Fease. Cloudier on Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
